room_title: Escape room "The Baker Street 5: A Sherlock Mystery" by Eye Spy Escape Rooms in Baton Rouge
room_description: Enter into the famous 221B Baker Street, the apartment of Sherlock Holmes. It is here you will find information concerning The Baker Street 5. This gang has tormented the residents of Baker Street far too long. Sherlock has put himself in harm's way going after a murderer within the group. Your task is to find them both before it is too late.
